            "bgtext": "#ffffff",
            "title_color": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "subtitle": "",
            "title": "Connect with an expert doctor. 24 hour response, 7 days a week.",
            "size_text": "h2",
            "text": "<p>Our TGA-approved doctors specialise in nicotine cessation and are dedicated to supporting your journey to become smoke-free. We understand quitting is challenging and requires personalised care. After reviewing your smoking history, your doctor will contact you to discuss your specific needs and create a tailored treatment plan designed to give you the best chance of long-term success.</p>",
